  "About 10%": "",
  "About 50%": "",
  "No savings; the same amount of data is stored": "",
  "Original: 1000 * 5000 = 5,000,000. With rank-50 approximation: 1000*50 + 50 + 50*5000 = 50,000 + 50 + 250,000 = 300,050. Savings: (5M - 300K)/5M = 94%. This is the power of low-rank approximation.": "",
  "A robotics engineer uses eigenvalue analysis to check stability of a discrete-time control system x(k+1) = Ax(k). The eigenvalues of A are 0.9, -0.8, and 0.5. Is the system stable?": "",
